OL,9,     FLove is in the air as bar stewards
OL,10,     Fand husbands 58-year-old Andy
OL,11,     FEdwards and 43-year-old Matt
OL,12,     FWalters celebrate their 14th
OL,13,     Fwedding anniversary.
OL,14,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,15,     FIn Fuengirola, we meet 38-year-old
OL,16,     FLondoner Lisa, who swapped her
OL,17,     Fbusy life as a beautician for a
OL,18,     Flower key life in Spain, and
OL,19,     Fdespite the sun is feeling a
OL,20,     Flittle lonely.
