OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FBurglary is one of the hardest
OL,7,     Fcrimes to secure a conviction for.
OL,8,     FIn this episode, the cops target
OL,9,     Fthieves and burglars who steal
OL,10,     Ffrom our homes, vehicles and
OL,11,     Fbusinesses.
OL,12,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FHair-raising encounters include a
OL,14,     Fpursuit of a determinedly
OL,15,     Fdangerous driver, and a father and
OL,16,     Fson driving at 50 miles an hour
OL,17,     Fover the limit with a load of cash
OL,18,     Fand mobile phones.
